data.name: rtbHelp.Text
data.value:
1) Select Sprite, Wall or Ceiling/floor to view the flag values for that object. 2) Select the number base Decimal, Hex or Binary for entering numbers into the 'Enter value' textbox. 3) Enter a number from 0 to 65535 decimal (0-FFFF hex) and press Enter to display the flags representing that number. 4) Check one or more items in the list, then click 'Calculate from checkboxes' to display the resulting value in the textbox (3). 5) Click to clear all the checked items in the list as well as the 'Enter value' textbox. 6) Click the checkbox, double-click the row or click the row and press Space to select/deselect items in the list. 7) Click any of the links to open your default browser to the corresponding webpage.
Use the Tab key to move between the different items in the form. Use the left/right arrow keys in the 'Mode' and 'Entry' groups to select one of the items in that group, and the up/down arrow keys to navigate the flags list.
